    "updated_at": "2015-09-29T20:13:18Z",
    "body": "Thanks for the feedback. A process fork seems like a plausible workaround. Could you be a bit more specific about what is going on with these events? I'd love to understand the problem with serialport a bit more in-depth. How are these events in Electron handled differently from a regular Node environment and what kind of modules are affected? How can you detect when these events walk up the message loop?\n"
  },
